<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>갈등과 조직성과 — 학술 근거 & HBR 사례</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  /* ── 기본 리셋 & 토큰 ──────────────────────────── */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --navy:       #0e1c2f;
    --navy-mid:   #162840;
    --navy-light: #1e3555;
    --gold:       #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #e8c96a;
    --gold-pale:  #f5e4a8;
    --teal:       #2a8090;
    --teal-light: #3dafbf;
    --green:      #2d9b6a;
    --green-light:#4dbf8a;
    --orange:     #d97a35;
    --red:        #c43e3e;
    --white:      #ffffff;
    --off-white:  #e8edf4;
    --gray:       #8899aa;
    --gray-light: #c5d0de;
    --paper:      #faf7f2;
    --ink:        #1a1a2e;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ── 배경 텍스처 ──────────────────────────────── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 28px, rgba(0,0,0,.018) 29px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 28px, rgba(0,0,0,.012) 29px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ── 레이아웃 ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px 80px;
  }

  /* ── 히어로 헤더 ──────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 -32px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--teal-light) 50%, var(--green-light) 100%);
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 32px 52px;
  }
  .hero-kicker {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .hero-kicker::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 28px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 46px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.12;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .hero-title span { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .hero-meta {
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.4);
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* ── 목차 바 ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .toc-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--navy-light);
    margin: 0 -32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .toc-item {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    transition: all .2s;
  }
  .toc-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .toc-item:hover { color: var(--white); background: rgba(201,168,76,.08); }
  .toc-item.active { color: var(--gold); }
  .toc-num {
    display: block;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  /* ── 섹션 헤더 ──────────────────────────────── */
  .section {
    margin-top: 64px;
  }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy);
  }
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(14,28,47,.1);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-bottom: -4px;
  }
  .section-text {}
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* ── 논문 카드 ──────────────────────────────── */
  .paper-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid #e0e4ec;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(14,28,47,.06);
    transition: box-shadow .25s, transform .2s;
  }
  .paper-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(14,28,47,.12);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .paper-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .paper-rank {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--gold);
    padding: 20px 18px;
    min-width: 64px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .paper-rank-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .paper-rank-circle {
    display: block;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 6px;
    opacity: .5;
  }
  .paper-meta-block {
    padding: 18px 22px 16px;
    flex: 1;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eef1f5;
  }
  .paper-title-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .paper-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 16.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.35;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .citation-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: flex-start;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .paper-authors {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .paper-journal {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--teal);
    letter-spacing: .04em;
  }
  .paper-body {
    padding: 18px 22px 20px;
  }

  /* 핵심 주장 박스 */
  .key-claim {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .key-claim::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: .3;
    position: absolute;
    top: -4px;
    left: 12px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* 포인트 리스트 */
  .points {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .points li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #2a2a3e;
  }
  .points li::before {
    content: '▸';
    color: var(--gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .points li strong { color: var(--navy); }

  /* 발표 팁 */
  .present-tip {
    background: #f0f7f4;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
    padding: 11px 14px;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #1a3a2a;
    line-height: 1.58;
  }
  .present-tip strong {
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* 유형 태그 */
  .tag-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .tag-pos  { background: #e6f7f0; color: #1a6b45; border: 1px solid #b2dfcc; }
  .tag-neg  { background: #fdf0ef; color: #8b2020; border: 1px solid #f0b8b8; }
  .tag-meta { background: #e8f3f7; color: #1a5068; border: 1px solid #a8d4e0; }
  .tag-hbr  { background: #fdf5e6; color: #7a4d10; border: 1px solid #e8c980; }
  .tag-amj  { background: #f0eff8; color: #3d2d7a; border: 1px solid #c4bee8; }

  /* ── HBR 카드 ───────────────────────────────── */
  .hbr-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .hbr-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid #e0e4ec;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(14,28,47,.06);
    transition: box-shadow .25s, transform .2s;
  }
  .hbr-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(14,28,47,.12);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .hbr-top {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 16px 22px 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .hbr-source {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .14em;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .hbr-year {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray);
  }
  .hbr-body {
    padding: 20px 22px 22px;
  }
  .hbr-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .hbr-author {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .hbr-url {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-decoration: none;
    background: #f0f8fa;
    border: 1px solid #c8e8f0;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    word-break: break-all;
    transition: background .2s;
  }
  .hbr-url:hover { background: #daf0f5; }
  .hbr-url::before { content: '🔗'; font-size: 11px; }
  .hbr-quote {
    background: #fffbf2;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 13px 16px;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #3a2a0a;
    line-height: 1.62;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  /* ── 요약 비교표 ────────────────────────────── */
  .summary-section {
    margin-top: 72px;
    background: var(--navy);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .summary-header {
    padding: 28px 32px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }
  .summary-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .summary-header p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .summary-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .summary-table thead tr {
    background: rgba(201,168,76,.15);
  }
  .summary-table th {
    padding: 11px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 500;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  }
  .summary-table td {
    padding: 11px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    vertical-align: middle;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .summary-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .summary-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,.03); }
  .td-title { color: var(--white) !important; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; }
  .td-cite {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .td-cite-hbr {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    background: var(--teal);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .td-part {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--teal-light);
  }

  /* ── 풋터 ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .footer {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #dde1ea;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .footer-left {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--gray);
    letter-spacing: .06em;
  }
  .footer-right {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── 반응형 ─────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .container { padding: 0 16px 60px; }
    .hero-inner { padding: 40px 16px 36px; }
    .toc-bar { display: none; }
    .paper-title-row { flex-direction: column; }
    .summary-table { font-size: 11px; }
    .summary-table th, .summary-table td { padding: 9px 10px; }
  }

  /* ── 애니메이션 ──────────────────────────────── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .paper-card, .hbr-card { animation: fadeUp .4s ease both; }
  .paper-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: .05s; }
  .paper-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .10s; }
  .paper-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: .15s; }
  .paper-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: .20s; }
  .paper-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: .25s; }
  .hbr-card:nth-child(1)  { animation-delay: .05s; }
  .hbr-card:nth-child(2)  { animation-delay: .10s; }
  .hbr-card:nth-child(3)  { animation-delay: .15s; }
  .hbr-card:nth-child(4)  { animation-delay: .20s; }

  /* ── divider ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .rule {
    border: none;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #dde1ea 30%, #dde1ea 70%, transparent);
    margin: 40px 0;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ────────────────── 히어로 ────────────────── -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-kicker">MBA 조직행동론 · 발표 참고자료</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      갈등이 팀과 조직의 성과에<br>
      <span>긍정적/부정적 영향을 미치는가?</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      우리 주장(YES)을 뒷받침하는 가장 많이 인용된 학술 논문 5편 +
      Harvard Business Review 핵심 사례 4편을 정리한 발표 참고 자료입니다.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="hero-badge">총 논문 5편 · 인용 합산 10,000+</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">HBR 사례 4편 · 1997–2025</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">YONSEI GSB · CMBA 10기</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ────────────────── 목차 바 ────────────────── -->
<nav class="toc-bar">
  <a href="#papers" class="toc-item active">
    <span class="toc-num">5</span>핵심 논문
  </a>
  <a href="#hbr" class="toc-item">
    <span class="toc-num">4</span>HBR 사례
  </a>
  <a href="#summary" class="toc-item">
    <span class="toc-num">↓</span>종합 비교
  </a>
</nav>

<!-- ────────────────── 본문 ────────────────── -->
<div class="container">

  <!-- ══ PART 1. 학술 논문 ══ -->
  <section id="papers" class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">1</div>
      <div class="section-text">
        <div class="section-label">Academic Papers · 학술 근거</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">가장 많이 인용된 갈등 관련 논문 5편</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 논문 ① -->
    <div class="paper-card">
      <div class="paper-header">
        <div class="paper-rank">
          <span class="paper-rank-num">①</span>
          <span class="paper-rank-circle"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="paper-meta-block">
          <div class="paper-title-row">
            <div class="paper-title">
              A Multimethod Examination of the Benefits and Detriments of Intragroup Conflict
            </div>
            <span class="citation-badge">인용 3,500+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="paper-authors">Karen A. Jehn</div>
          <div class="paper-journal">Administrative Science Quarterly, Vol. 40, pp. 256–282 · 1995</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="paper-body">
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag tag-pos">과업 갈등 긍정</span>
          <span class="tag tag-amj">AMJ 최우수논문상 2회</span>
          <span class="tag tag-meta">갈등 유형 최초 체계화</span>
        </div>
        <div class="key-claim">
          과업 갈등은 적절할 경우 의사결정 품질과 혁신을 향상시킨다.
          갈등의 '유형'에 따라 성과 방향이 달라진다.
        </div>
        <ul class="points">
          <li>105개 작업 집단 대상 다중 방법론(인터뷰·설문·관찰) 연구</li>
